{"tid":235934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無長期服務金，我工人詛咒我爸媽落地獄","createTime":"2017-05-09T11:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T14:35:44.000Z","uid":109492,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"443ac840ce1337a46b8c2d10a1f256c3f822c757","tid":235934,"uid":109492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"事源係咁，我屋企工人姐姐平時都惡底，不過佢做野快快手，同我地屋企關係算正常。一做就做左12年，有日佢話要辭職，我阿媽話okay，不過無長期服務金，佢一開始話唔緊要，自己問過勞工署，知道係無。<br />\n<br />\n之後唔知佢係咪愈諗條氣愈唔順，主動同我媽講：你以前應承過畀我！ 我阿媽話屋企環境無以前咁好，所以唔會畀。佢之後態度一直都唔友善，但唔知去到咁憎我地屋企。臨走個陣留低封信畀佢地，話佢地會落地獄，成世都會好多病！<br />\n<br />\n同佢雖然無幾句，不過諗返佢原來咁憎我地，都幾唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05615576a58ad54c2e9fd6d3037ca05caab3731a","tid":235934,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"應承左人做唔到仲有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092bb91f0eb22da17db9f2f242c93cf190f03a74","tid":235934,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"冇誠信，冇得怪人"},{"pid":"5d77a6743404df942f187275a4b37c282f13487b","tid":235934,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca1d98cefb7813a43ec38a835a5f74181ab99613","tid":235934,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b32158bfbe7df09c270481bdda874c20d4a4655","tid":235934,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"應承左人唔俾抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f025924bad03b530e68822b3d44594961210f43e","tid":235934,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"地獄就落緊架啦 睇下第幾層<br />\n利申：賓主左廿年 感情好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27af8d24998e972b402a440509d828