":235934,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"唔係做夠7年就要比long service 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aa276e55953a769fe66fda0b1d45ac98af8b12","tid":235934,"uid":35445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"老闆: 今年個市唔好，之前應承過既長期服務金當我無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f946e1a32905b1482f3d1d7b17140be012fa657","tid":235934,"uid":103003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"我之前都有個工人姐姐 <br />\n佢同我地關係好好<br />\n我當正佢係我第二個mama <br />\n佢同我地生活左都有16年 最後無長期服務金 佢都肯<br />\n 佢好好 我好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del><br />\n直到宜加雖然佢無做 但我同佢都間唔中出街食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又會請番佢食野"},{"pid":"8e6727f1c42ca0dda4a96f8c02a875e11c9f2414","tid":235934,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"話屋企環境好就唔比，賺得多又唔見你手鬆少少比多幾個錢，現家做咁多年比筆錢佢當係人情都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bfff0f5434c615c356ff04da7421b96d23e118","tid":235934,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"廢老唔落地獄唔通去迪士尼咩"},{"pid":"79ab7131cf1c75cf32dfa0b11b89f7287d6d0325","tid":235934,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"自己辭職係冇長期服務金"},{"pid":"a1e39f3d8bf30e0341d7a65972bd22b505ef8a78","tid":235934,"uid":35445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都有個工人姐姐 <br />\n佢同我地關係好好<br />\n我當正佢係我第二個mama <br />\n佢同我地生活左都有16年 最後無長期服務金 佢都肯<br />\n 佢好好 我好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del><br />\n直到宜加雖然佢無做 但我同佢都間唔<span style=\"color: red;\">中出</span>街食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又會請番佢食野</blockquote><br />\n我認我心邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d245103d09fec60b44755ba09171aef48bc705","tid":235934,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"希望佢毒你全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf5cc2ac901cc6a30d5a2327baad421cc9d822e","tid":235934,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d839b2596884809a443fc1bf8dfd87badaad7499","tid":235934,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"做左12年先知比人呃左<br />\n如果唔係佢信你有長期服務金 <br />\n一早搵左第2家人黎做啦<br />\n<br />\n佢講句落地獄算好撚友善嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街"},{"pid":"3cecdf6ab287fa1a79c9e45b413fb24e90ca404d","tid":235934,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"一個12年，應承左人但就只係畀2個月人工<br />\n一個16年就直頭1蚊都唔畀<br />\n<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}